name: 4th event at Sector BDR2132
description:
"It is a cumulative transfer of information, to put it in the simplest sense", said the professor. "It is nothing that I've seen before. Then again, we have never been here before either. According to our rough abductions, this is quite a common occurrence in this area. As long as we are careful, we should be able to pass through safely."

-----The "town" is produced by a random assignment of "buildings" in a phyllotactic spiral, while the swarm is via a random curve spline generation. Modeled and rendered in Blender----------
